summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning; amending Chapter 23.32 of the Seattle Municipal Code at page 188 of the Official Land Use Map to rezone property located at 9125 Yukon Avenue South from Single Family 5000 (SF 5000) to Lowrise 1 (L1). (Petition by Tony Case, C.F. 310852, DPD Project 3006392)
